Uses of Package
kp.company

  • Packages that use kp.company 
    Package Description
    kp.company
    The classes in this package represent Business Layer.
    kp.company.hibernate
    The classes in this package represent the Hibernate implementation of the Persistence Layer.
    kp.company.jdbc
    The classes in this package represent the JDBC implementation of the Persistence Layer.
    kp.company.jpa
    The classes in this package represent the JPA implementation of the Persistence Layer.
    kp.company.util
    The classes in this package represent application utilities.
    kp.company.validation
    The classes in this package represent the set of Validator objects the Business Layer makes available to the Presentation Layer.
    kp.company.web
    The classes in this package represent the Web Presentation Layer.
